	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. A cena libellum huncce<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName ref="p1974" cert="high">Luthers</persName> "Kurtz Bekentnis"; s. oben <ref target="file12018">Nr. 1971</ref>, Anm. 20.</note>, tantopere a te desideratum,<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Siehe oben <ref target="file12077">Nr. 2030</ref>, 12-18; 2044, 27-35.</note> a <persName ref="p1055" cert="high">Frechto</persName> nostro accepi,<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Aus <placeName ref="l513" cert="high">Ulm</placeName>. Ein entsprechender Begleitbrief an <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Blarer</persName> ist unbekannt.</note> qui potestatem fecit mihi eum<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b">eum <hi>über unlesbar gemachtem Wort.</hi></note> ad te mittendi, sed ea lege, ut, ubi usus eo fueris, rursum ad nos remittas; paucissima enim extare exemplaria, quamquam mihi plura plurimis extare videntur, si vel unicum extet.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu pro christiana tua prudentia omnia vide, ut circumspecte agas nihilque <persName ref="p1974" cert="high">Luthero</persName>, qui nec audire nos nec respondere nobis dignatur, sed omnia ecclesiis Christi scribes, illis vos<note xml:id="fnc" type="footnote" n="c">vos <hi>korrigiert aus</hi> nos.</note> modestissime purgaturus.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego tumultuanter tantoque animi dolore legi, ut plane iam, quid legerim, exciderit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed vale cum tuis et domino nos diligenter commenda.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nequeo plura et spero te superiores meas literas<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Oben <ref target="file12091">Nr. 2044</ref> vom 5. Dezember.</note>, quas per <persName ref="8055" type="auto_name">Saram</persName><note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Eine Verwandte <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Blarers</persName>? Die Tochter Sara von <persName ref="p8178" cert="high">Thomas Blarer</persName> (s. <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Blarer</persName> BW III 70. 884) wird hier kaum in Frage kommen.</note> misi, accepisse.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iterum vale.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">13. decembris 1544.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus Amb. Bl.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si iam antea libellum habes,<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Hatte Bullinger bereits damals das ihm von <persName ref="p8317" cert="high">Markus Crodel</persName> zugesandte Exemplar (s. oben <ref target="file12084">Nr. 2037</ref>, Anm. 3) erhalten?</note> hunc quamprimum remitte; nullus enim prorsus apud nos illum legit.<pb type="edition" next="585"/></s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tragica scribunt<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">Nicht ermittelt.</note> Esselingiacenses de duce Wirtemp[ergensi]<note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8"><persName ref="p9780" cert="high">Herzog Ulrich von Württemberg</persName>.</note>, quod miseros quosdam Acteones<note xml:id="fn9" type="footnote" n="9">D.h. Jäger (nach dem Jäger Akteon oder Aktaion in der griech. Mythologie; vgl. Albert <hi>Schachter,</hi> in: <bibl>DNP</bibl> I 414).</note> exocularit<note xml:id="fn10" type="footnote" n="10">Vgl. oben <ref target="file12083">Nr. 2036</ref> mit Anm. 13; 2044, 38-40.</note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse vor S. 102:]</note>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bullingero suo Tiguri.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Maister Hainrich Bullinger zuͦ Zuͤrich.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zuͤrich.</s>
				</p>
